snippet.title: Rocket League High Octane Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the High Octane Trailer!
Learn more here: http://www.rocketleague.com/news/highoctane-whiplash/

Octane is speeding beyond Sovereign Heights to islands far beyond the Soccar Arena. Meanwhile, Whiplash enters the pitch in both Rocket League and Rocket League Sideswipe as part of High Octane! Starting today through December 3, complete High Octane Quests to earn a slew of Items in both Rocket League and Rocket League Sideswipe.

#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueHighOctane #RocketLeagueWhiplash
